  stimulus_text = 'The following excerpt is from the preface to a book on nineteenth-century fashion: "The world of nineteenth-century textiles was a fascinating one, full of rich textures, bold patterns, and intricate designs. Women—and men—of the time, took great pride in their dress, often choosing fabrics and styles that reflected their social status, their individual tastes, or simply their desire for the most elaborate and eye-catching garments. However, in this complex and ever-changing world, the art of dressmaking itself was a difficult one, requiring great skill and precision. This is why many women sought the help of professional seamstresses, who would assist them in fashioning garments that would make them feel confident and elegant." Which choice best states the main idea of this excerpt?',
